shelldone (1.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Enriched notification messages across all channels
  * Auto-notify now captures full command with arguments
  * Discord embeds with structured fields, footer, and timestamp
  * Telegram messages with HTML formatting and metadata
  * Email body with structured key=value metadata
  * WhatsApp context line with project, host, and branch
  * Generic webhook payload with full metadata fields
  * AI hook exit code mapping for error stop reasons
  * alert-bg sets metadata and fixes false-green unknown status
  * Duration formatting shows <1s instead of 0s
  * Word-boundary-aware command truncation
  * Locale-independent 24-hour timestamp format

 -- Naresh Sekar <nareshnavinash@gmail.com>  Tue, 17 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000

shelldone (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * BREAKING: Rebranded from cli-alert to shelldone
  * All environment variables renamed: CLI_ALERT_* → SHELLDONE_*
  * Backward compatibility shim for CLI_ALERT_* env vars
  * Config directory migration from ~/.config/cli-alert to ~/.config/shelldone

 -- Naresh Sekar <nareshnavinash@gmail.com>  Tue, 17 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000

shelldone (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Multi-AI CLI hook support: Codex CLI, Gemini CLI, GitHub Copilot CLI, Cursor
  * Per-AI toggle system (shelldone toggle claude off, etc.)
  * Shared hook library (lib/ai-hook-common.sh)
  * Auto-detect and install all AI hooks (shelldone setup ai-hooks)
  * Uninstall now removes all AI CLI hooks

 -- Naresh Sekar <nareshnavinash@gmail.com>  Mon, 16 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000

